					<h2 class="headline" itemprop="name"><a href="http://the-gadgeteer.com/2015/02/19/montar-car-mount-serbag-messenger-bag-sjcam-action-cam-and-more-gadget-review-updates/" rel="bookmark">Montar car mount, Serbag messenger bag, SJCAM action cam and more &#8211; Gadget review updates</a></h2>
					<div class="byline small">
						<span class="post_author_intro">by</span> <span class="post_author" itemprop="author"><a href="http://the-gadgeteer.com/author/julie/">Julie Strietelmeier</a></span>
