<p><a href="http://the-gadgeteer.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/timeswirl.jpg" rel="dofollow"><img class="alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-170571" src="http://the-gadgeteer.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/timeswirl-150x150.jpg" alt="timeswirl" width="150" height="150" /></a></p> <p>This week Raul Sanchez adds updates to five of his past reviews to let us know how the products are still working for him. Click through to see his list of updated reviews and then scroll to the bottom of each of the listed reviews to read his latest update.</p> <p> <a href="http://the-gadgeteer.com/2015/02/19/montar-car-mount-serbag-messenger-bag-sjcam-action-cam-and-more-gadget-review-updates/#more-174091" class="more-link" rel="dofollow">[click to continue&hellip;]</a></p> 				</div>
